<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Welcome to Transcendence üèì</title>
    <style>
      /* GENERAL RESET */
      body {
        font-family: "Arial", sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        max-width: 620px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0;
        background: #0a0c10;
        color: #d6d6d6;
      }

      /* ARCANE DIAGONAL TEXTURE LIKE YOUR CARDS */
      .card-bg {
        background: repeating-linear-gradient(
          135deg,
          #0f1218 0px,
          #0f1218 3px,
          #0d1014 3px,
          #0d1014 6px
        );
      }

      .container {
        margin: 40px auto;
        border-radius: 12px;
        overflow: hidden;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      }

      /* HEADER */
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 30px 0;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #11141a, #0d1016);
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      }

      .logo {
        font-size: 32px;
        font-weight: bold;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        color: #ffffff;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        font-family: "Courier New", monospace;
      }

      /* CONTENT */
      .content {
        padding: 35px;
      }

      h2 {
        color: #ffffff;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 26px;
        margin-bottom: 25px;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
      }

      p {
        color: #c9c9c9;
        margin-bottom: 14px;
      }

      ul {
        margin: 20px 0;
        padding-left: 20px;
      }

      li {
        margin-bottom: 12px;
      }

      strong {
        color: #ffffff;
      }

      /* ICON AREA */
      .welcome-image {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }

      .welcome-image span {
        font-size: 64px;
        display: inline-block;
        transition: transform 0.25s ease;
      }

      .welcome-image span:hover {
        transform: scale(1.12);
      }

      .highlight {
        color: #ffffff;
        font-weight: bold;
        text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
      }

      /* BUTTON MATCHING YOUR PONG MENU */
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 14px 28px;
        background: #ffffff;
        color: #000000 !important;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 6px;
        border: 2px solid #ffffff;
        font-weight: bold;
        font-size: 15px;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        transition: all 0.25s ease;
      }

      .button:hover {
        background: #dcdcdc;
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
      }

      /* FOOTER */
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px 0;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0d1016, #0b0d12);
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #8c8c8c;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="container card-bg">
      <div class="header">
        <div class="logo">Transcendence üèì</div>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <h2>Welcome to the Game!</h2>

        <div class="welcome-image">
          <span>üèì</span>
        </div>

        <p>Welcome aboard!</p>

        <p>
          You're now part of <span class="highlight">Transcendence</span>, the
          arena where battles are fast, scoreboards are alive, and every match
          is a step toward mastery.
        </p>

        <p>Here‚Äôs what you can do right away:</p>

        <ul>
          <li>üéØ <strong>Challenge your friends</strong> in duels</li>
          <li>üèÜ <strong>Join tournaments</strong> and rise to the top</li>
          <li>üìà <strong>Track your stats</strong> as you improve</li>
        </ul>

        <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px">
          <a href="<%= link %>" class="button">START PLAYING</a>
        </p>

        <p>Have fun out there!</p>

        <p>The Transcendence Team</p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>¬© <%= (new Date()).getFullYear() %> Transcendence</p>
        <p>
          You received this email because you created an account on
          Transcendence.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
